***Asks Him To Resign ***Says Nigeria Media Must Not Fail, Cowed When All Others Fail ABUJA – Presidential candidate of the African Democratic Congress (ADC) Dumebi Kachiukwu has declared the All Progressives Congress (APC) administration under President Muhammadu Buhari has failed Nigeria abysmally, called on citizens who are in the majority to rise and salvage the country from total collapse. Addressing an emergency press conference of the party’s National Working committee last night in Abuja, the ADC standard bearer said 2023 is too far to address the systemic failure of the government. Details later…